  {Th}/ST1                    ST1                   ---
  {Th}/ST2                    ST2                   ---
  {Ac}/ST0                    Blood                 0.462
  {Ac}/ST1                    Blood                 0.462
  {Ac}/ST2                    Blood                 0.462
