  Blood                   Liver1                    11.6
  Blood                   T-bone-S                  3.49
  Blood                   C-bone-S                  3.49
  Blood                   Kidneys1                  0.466
  Blood                   Kidneys2                  0.116
  Blood                   UB-con                    1.63
  Blood                   RC-con                    0.303
  Blood                   Testes                    0.0082
  Blood                   Ovaries                   0.0026
  Blood                   ST0                       10.0
 #Blood                   ST1                       1.67        # fix
  Blood                   ST2                       0.466
  Liver1                  SI-conRe                  0.0006
  Liver1                  Liver2                    0.0225
